title: Episode 112: Feat. Maino
itunes:title: Episode 112: Feat. Maino
description:
Maino sits with the ladies of Lip Service and spoke on a wide range of topics including how everyone envisions their wedding day, sex robots, hiring private detectives, and when eating too many weed cookies goes wrong. Everyone shares a story from their life in which they confess to being a hoe at one time or the other. Things get heated between Maino and Lore'l after a constant exchange of low blows.
